column5: At least until he realised what was going on.  just a shade over 11lbs    the view from overhead
Nice one,   Good to hear things picked up a little after our chat.  we tucked our tails at 11
Thats a nice eye G. Well done fellas.
yup that's a beaut. I have caught a few closing  in on 10 lbs while fishing for musky...you would swear (and I have) that you are reeling in a branch off bottom
Walleye up here do roll overs and headshakes.  Funny how its different on different bodies of water  No wet socks here
